node_modules
**/node_modules
# The Tauri wizard (apps/wizard) is never part of the web/worker images; excluding
# it keeps its multi-GB Rust target/ out of the `COPY . .` build context. It is a
# pnpm workspace member, but like packages/sealed|packaging it is simply absent
# from the deps-stage COPY list, which --frozen-lockfile tolerates.
apps/wizard
**/.next
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.turbo
